45
00:03:39,206 --> 00:03:44,906
"Pelanggaran Merah dan Hitam: Kebangkitan."

46
00:03:44,931 --> 00:03:48,030
"Hospital Pusat Haido."

47
00:03:48,031 --> 00:03:50,430
Patutkah saya periksa tingkat dua?

48
