74
00:05:59,631 --> 00:06:01,930
FBI?

75
00:06:01,931 --> 00:06:03,530
Itu bermaksud tempat Rena Mizunashi

76
00:06:03,531 --> 00:06:07,630
sedang tidur lena ialah di hospital ini.

77
